        },
        {
            "_id": "tUBKQu5RqbND3xIi",
            "img": "systems/sf2e/icons/actions/Passive.webp",
            "name": "Mosaic Touch",
            "sort": 500000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "passive"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The soul's touch Strike unravels living targets into their components, leaving grievous wounds like acid burns. A living creature that takes Hit Point damage from the mosaic soul's touch Strike and must attempt a @Check[fortitude|dc:17] save or take @Damage[2d6[persistent,acid]] damage.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "value": []
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
        {
            "_id": "GIS3fINcWyqTDJCu",
            "img": "systems/sf2e/icons/actions/TwoActions.webp",
            "name": "Swirling Colors",
            "sort": 600000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The mosaic soul's colors shimmer and invert in terrible flashes. All other creatures within a @Template[type:emanation|distance:30] must attempt a @Check[fortitude|dc:19] save (mosaic souls are immune to this ability). The mosaic soul's strange light aura casts bright light until the start of its next turn.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Dazzled] until the end of its next turn.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Blinded] until the end of its next turn.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is blinded until the end of its next turn and @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Fascinated] for 1 minute.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "value": [
                        "light",
                        "visual"
                    ]
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        }
